\v 37 Itsho njalo iNkosi uJehova: Langalokhu ngizacelwa yindlu kaIsrayeli, ukuthi ngiyenzele khona\x + 14.3.\x*; ngizabandisa ngabantu\x + 36.10.\x* njengomhlambi\x + 34.31.\x*.
\v 38 Njengomhlambi ongcwele\x + 34.31.\x*\x + Isa. 66.20. Roma 12.1. 15.16.\x*, njengomhlambi weJerusalema emikhosini yawo emisiweyo\x + 2 Lan. 35.7.\x*, ngokunjalo imizi echithekileyo izagcwala ngemihlambi yabantu\x + 34.31.\x*. Khona bazakwazi ukuthi ngiyiN\nd kosi\x + 36.11.\x*\nd*.